{"tid":416763,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"覆核王：太遲又話不可干預中央","createTime":"2017-09-28T05:01:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-19T12:14:12.000Z","uid":25558,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"a273bc6a52fe8d293e5cd5b550bcd4e00799c488","tid":416763,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T05:01:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20170928/20166384\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20170928%2F20166384&d=iSYwik3gVh0G1Y9y2f78fROFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=cbd4a5df\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20170928%2F20166384&h=b959ba60\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20170928/20166384</a><br />\n<br />\n覆核王：太遲又話不可干預中央<br />\n<br />\n4,260<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20170928/large/0927yiu7002.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170928%2Flarge%2F0927yiu7002.jpg&h=9fda106b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■呂智恆（左）及郭卓堅（右）<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】申請人一方曾於聆訊中表示本案有多個情況特殊，法庭應盡早受理，例如可迫使特區政府考慮其他合法方案、避免訴訟拖延影響高鐵通車及立法後始發現政策越權，又指若一地兩檢安排完成後始遭市民成功挑戰，勢將浪費巨額公帑，並令中港兩地要倉卒提出替代方案，造成不便。惟法官指上述擔憂只牽涉公共開支及行政安排，屬於政治議題，應由兩地政府、而非法庭解決。<br />\n<br />\n申請人郭卓堅及呂智恆昨日均表示會考慮上訴。郭卓堅自言不反對一地兩檢，他只是反對在本港執行內地法律。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n兩人考慮上訴<br />\n<br />\n郭卓堅不滿法庭指他太早覆核，「如果我哋太遲，佢又會話中央同意咗，香港唔可以干預中央」，指法庭「將個龍門搬來搬去」。<br />\n<br />\n呂則指以現時本港政治環境而言，在黑箱作業下一地兩檢「冇可能過唔到」，故必須及早覆核，同時會由10月1日起召集市民參與不合作運動，抵制中資黨產。<br />\n<br />\n另外，法官頒令申請人需要支付政府一方訟費。由於呂智恆及李嘉廉獲批法援，而張德榮及曾健成在未獲法援後已退出訴訟，故只得郭卓堅要自行承擔。郭揚言公民抗命，不會付堂費，但會眾籌律師費。<br />\n<br />\n■記者楊家樂  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n稱未立法申請言之尚早　官指暫難言違憲拒受理一地兩檢覆核<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n涉失教師資格留校　興德前校長助理保釋"},{"pid":"22ea979c81a91533742941fe33ad27802208174c","tid":416763,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T05:08:51.000Z","msg":"郭生 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b21271461c093c5c3624b834a4c9c0460c34d5a6","tid":416763,"uid":25825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T05:10:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02d70fa28b584145d62f81f70d872b196ed8457b","tid":416763,"uid":81876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T05:12:43.000Z","msg":"法院有可能就假設事情作法律見解嗎？<br />\n<br />\n有無法律JJ解答"},{"pid":"e64520b63602c54781a4a4d447fd0c2d82329c42","tid":416763,"uid":37735,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T05:14:50.000Z","msg":"郭生算係咁<br />\n<br />\n佢都唔知揹住幾多條呢d數<br />\n<br />\n比泛民，左膠，熱狗果堆 做得更多"},{"pid":"7539d252e8b081fbe0afc992ccc5978724f39426","tid":416763,"uid":49588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T05:18:11.000Z","msg":"香港人支持你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86cfcaccd2f94c3f5c86af72ba5059d351a1e7fc","tid":416763,"uid":39685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T05:36:14.000Z","msg":"respect<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7315747a4d39dd2649e1e71952c509dd8341eca9","tid":416763,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T05:38:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c5fae492c83ce545a0c8fef83d710ba3db5bd20","tid":416763,"uid":108